RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO, B.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM LBTBS_CONTRACT_BORROWERS A, OLTM_CUSTOMER B WHERE B.CUSTOMER_NO = A.CUSTOMER_NO AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? UNION SELECT 'ALL', 'ALL CUSTOMERS' FROM DUAL WHERE ? = 'ALL' UNION SELECT A.COUNTERPARTY, B.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTM_CUSTOMER B WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND B.CUSTOMER_NO = A.COUNTERPARTY

SELECT A.COMPONENT, A.DESCRIPTION, b.slab_or_tier, b.rate_or_amt FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_FEE A, LFTMS_FEE_DEFINITION B WHERE A.PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(?) AND NVL(A.STOP_ASSOCIATION, 'N') = 'N' AND Fee_Rule IN (SELECT C.FEE_COMPONENT FROM LFTMS_FEE_DEFINITION C WHERE C.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND C.RECORD_STAT = 'O') AND A.Fee_Rule = b.fee_component AND BASIS_AMOUNT_TAG <> 'USERINPUT' AND A.FEE_RULE_TYPE = 'M'
SELECT A.CCY_CODE, A.CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN A WHERE A.CCY_CODE = ? and A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A'
